{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a1f29829c1","title":"毛泽东转发华东局关于镇反应注意之点的电报的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3852cf4d95","index":0,"year":1951,"month":1,"day":24,"articleId":"a1f29829c1"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e557e3997b","type":"title","text":"毛泽东转发华东局关于镇反应注意之点的电报的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a1f29829c1"},{"id":"8bc1fbfb16","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a1f29829c1"},{"id":"e78cb7e52c","type":"appellation","text":"子恢，剑英，小平，仲勋，一波，高岗同志：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a1f29829c1"},{"id":"e4b68696b4","type":"paragraph","text":"华东局给福建省委电所说肃反应注意之点，我以为是对的。即为了打落敌焰，伸张民气，对匪首惯匪恶霸及确有证据的重要特务和会门头子，应当放手杀几批。为了不致弄错，使自己陷于被动，对尚无证据的特务及会门头子，应当进行侦察，取得确证，而不要随便捕人杀人。分清这两种情况的界限是必要的，请你们转知所属注意为盼。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a1f29829c1"},{"id":"acbd953bbb","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东一月廿四日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a1f29829c1"}],"page":{"id":"fe79829ea0","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a1f29829c1","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}